data.description: Here is your chance to own your spacious 3-bedroom 2 bath haven featuring over 1800 sqft! This charming home boasts brand new carpet in bedrooms and fresh paint in entire home. Located in a serene neighborhood, you will enjoy the short commute to I-295, shopping and NAS Jax. This home features an open layout, large backyard for entertaining and spacious bedrooms. Guest bathroom features a walk-in tub and new LVP flooring. Owner suite features a spacious room with walk in closet and separate tub/shower. Call today for your showing.
